XML configfiles:
	You need libxml version 2 to use the configfile features of ices.
Reencoding:
	You need libmp3lame.a and lame.h to use the reencoding features of
	ices. Also, make bloody sure that your mp3 files are ok, otherwize
	the reencoding will make ices crash.
	A good tool to use for mp3 checking is mp3check.
Embedded languages for playlist handling:
	Support perl and python scripts.
Stable bitrate:
	Uses libshout.
